LinkedIn Assistant: Automate Your LinkedIn Tasks.

‚ö° Efficient Scraping: Quickly and efficiently scrape thousands of LinkedIn profiles from a search and export into csv. Supports the general search page and the linkedin recruiter search page.

‚ö° Ranking: Use the power of AI to rank through all the profiles to sort the best match to the top of your list
